[DhtmlXQ_comment9]And as can be seen from the diagram, after red plays the palcorner cannon, the opening is basically fixed:||the 56 Cannons with Left Side Horse variation vs the screen horse defense.||It is a fashionable opening.||The main character of this opening is that is less aggressive and is much slower paced, with more emphasis on the deployment of forces. ||The advantage gained is accumulated in small amounts. 　[/DhtmlXQ_comment9]
[DhtmlXQ_comment12]Playing C8+4 would be to red's slight advantage. Red would also have more pawns.[/DhtmlXQ_comment12]
